{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"61-pehelwaan-ji","title":"Pehelwaan Ji","description":"Pehelwaan Ji was a bit of a bully. But Gappu soon took care of that. Read this amusing story about their bout of wrestling!","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Manisha Chaudhry"],"illustrators":["Ajit Narayan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/61-pehelwaan-ji"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722698/size3/98bcdcf0cb7fb7abb4210429783d8707.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/722698/size6/98bcdcf0cb7fb7abb4210429783d8707.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/748/size6/f6340438abc0a5abb99ea7a88e43f60c.jpg","text":"Pehelwaan ji!","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/749/size6/d6923481e112550e37c8f91d7a14e233.jpg","text":"He drinks ten litres of milk everyday.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/750/size6/bfc8679e2bc99b2262a9a17bb1ece670.jpg","text":"He eats fifty rotis.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/751/size6/8ef3b17259f82229c8b50196f658d480.jpg","text":"He lifts weights of a hundred kilos.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/752/size6/8a6360d4d934d5cbf885843fd2d7a367.jpg","text":"He walks with a swagger.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/753/size6/768a6f4c240627113514a39b140e0310.jpg","text":"He orders all the children about.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/754/size6/771c9388da7e53e0c0e7a8fffe08610d.jpg","text":"One day, Gappu said, “Will you wrestle with me?”","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/755/size6/7a655af45002bed26dfcaa78d4701342.jpg","text":"Pehelwaan ji laughed. And then agreed.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/756/size6/89245ed1c405bf76ca193e03285ab545.jpg","text":"Both of them slapped their thighs!","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/757/size6/b4e81974202ef63de305e50c2ec9e30a.jpg","text":"Pehelwaan ji caught hold of Gappu.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/758/size6/0293e12ae3a3c5f56d9689f789903e5c.jpg","text":"Gappu tickled him in the stomach.","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/759/size6/1782e99fc0500fe423303099b6ec5e7e.jpg","text":"Hee…Heee…Heeee… Pehelwaan ji jumped!","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/760/size6/b420b8a55e1c596e72282ff77420b550.jpg","text":"As Gappu tickled him, Pehelwaan ji began to dance.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/761/size6/cb0fd0a2c6d842e85383a737946f570f.jpg","text":"Ha…Ha…Hee…Hee…Hoo…Hoo…\nPehelwaan ji rolled about helplessly. And he ran away.","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/762/size6/8f5c3b50dc44cc9ae623d4394e28d32c.jpg","text":"The kids are not scared of him any more. He is scared of them.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":101}}